sentences: Olen juba öelnud, et me peame sööma.
Tema naine ei taha, et me söögiks midagi sellest.
Kui sa tõesti oled näljane, siis sööme.
context: 'Sööme' is the first person plural form of the verb 'sööma', which means to eat. It is used when more than one person is involved in eating something, including the speaker and at least one other person.
